001package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.table.filters;
002
003/**
004 * Defines filtering strategies for table elements.
005 *
006 * <p>These strategies determine how table elements are filtered,
007 * allowing selection and deselection actions.
008 *
009 * <p>Currently, there are no direct usages, but it is intended
010 * to be used in conjunction with filtering functionalities
011 * such as {@link CellFilterFunction}.
012 *
013 * @author Cyborg Code Syndicate üíçüë®üíª
014 */
015public enum FilterStrategy {
016
017   /**
018    * Selects only the specified elements, deselecting others.
019    */
020   SELECT_ONLY,
021
022   /**
023    * Selects the specified elements without affecting others.
024    */
025   SELECT,
026
027   /**
028    * Selects all available elements.
029    */
030   SELECT_ALL,
031
032   /**
033    * Unselects the specified elements without affecting others.
034    */
035   UNSELECT,
036
037   /**
038    * Unselects all elements.
039    */
040   UNSELECT_ALL
041}
